{
  "stem": "1419.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew it was something coming, because the airfield we were working on was striped by American planes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were so happy to see it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The German guards, they were hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were telling-- they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We  were not hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We, we, we, we didn't-- we, we didn't want to hide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were just looking up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They come to stripe the airfield.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were shooting at the German planes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was-- [SOBS] it was quite a sight, you know, to see.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But anyway-- I'm getting-- I'm getting emotional.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But anyway, the 25th of April, we were supposed to march out from this particular camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We knew it was already the end of the war almost.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't know how long it will last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took out 10 people from the camp again, some young, young guys, to bring some bread from the-- from the work, or from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was between them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to the kitchen to see a whole bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like a dream to see a bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- so I took a bread, and I put it under my coat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And me, stupid, I was quite, you know, skinny.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sticked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The bread sticked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The minute I came back with the bread, they saw that I-- that I had the bread on me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They pulled me out, and they took-- and they took-- they took me on the-- on the Appelplatz in the-- in the center.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they start to beat me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They beat me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, why did you took the bread?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did you take the bread?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I needed the bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
